<td box="[910,1138,1239,1322]" gridcol="3" gridrow="3" pageId="6" pageNumber="229">distinctly sinuate anteriorly (Fig. 16)</td>
<td box="[1180,1417,1239,1322]" gridcol="4" gridrow="3" pageId="6" pageNumber="229">distinctly sinuate anteriorly (Fig. 18)</td>
