<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1436,1933,2031]" pageId="6" pageNumber="229">
Additionally from all currently known species of genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Mulsant &amp; Rey" authorityYear="1869" box="[836,940,1933,1959]" class="Insecta" family="Aphodiidae" genus="Agrilinus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="229" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
